  <li>ë°©ë¬¸í•˜ê¸°</li>
  <li>ì˜ˆì•½í•˜ê¸° ğŸ‘‰ ë°©ë¬¸í•œ ì •ì ì— ì—°ê²°ë˜ì–´ ìˆëŠ” ë‹¤ìŒ ë…¸ë“œë“¤ (ìì‹ ë…¸ë“œ)
    <ul>
      <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vertex[nowNode]</code> ëŒë©´ì„œ í˜„ì¬ ë°©ë¬¸í•œ ì •ì ì¸ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">nowNode</code>ì™€ ì—°ê²°ë˜ì–´ ìˆëŠ” ì •ì ë“¤(ìì‹ ì •ì  = <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vertex[nowNode][i]</code>) ì¤‘ì—ì„œ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">if (!found[child])</code> ì˜ˆì•½ëœ ì ì´ ì—†ëŠ” ì •ì ì„ íì— ë„£ì–´ ì˜ˆì•½í•œë‹¤.
        <ul>
          <li>íì— ì‚½ì…</li>
